---
// ============================================================================
// AdsterraNative.astro
// ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Renders Adsterra's "Native Banner" ad unit — a self-sizing ad that blends
// into surrounding content rather than a fixed iframe size. Placed inside
// the main content column on select pages (not sitewide) to balance
// monetization against page speed and a clean reading experience.
//
// Why this loads safely:
//   - The script tag is `async`, so it never blocks the page from
//     rendering or delays Core Web Vitals (LCP/FID/CLS) while it loads.
//   - It renders into a dedicated <div id="container-..."> rather than
//     using document.write, so it can't break page layout the way older
//     ad network scripts sometimes do.
//   - A fixed-height wrapper reserves space before the ad loads, so it
//     doesn't cause layout shift (CLS) once it does.
//
// This is a separate component from AdSlot.astro (which is AdSense-only)
// because Adsterra and AdSense are two independent networks with their own
// script/markup formats — keeping them in separate components means either
// network can be added, removed, or swapped without touching the other.
// ============================================================================
---

<div class="ad-slot ad-slot--native my-8 flex min-h-[100px] w-full justify-center">
  <div id="container-176d1a0c8f2aeed54b5a122e9c64b94f" class="w-full max-w-2xl"></div>
</div>

<script is:inline async data-cfasync="false" src="https://pl30187697.effectivecpmnetwork.com/176d1a0c8f2aeed54b5a122e9c64b94f/invoke.js"></script>
